    Class to represent a movie and it's associated attributes. To support mapping of this object to DynamoDB, the id is defined as a String As a rule, attribute names must be stored in "Title Case", where the first letter of each word is capitalized and all other letters are lower case. As the movie class serves as the primary holder of attributes, enforcing "Title Case" attribute names is handled within this class.
